OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FThe European Council has formally
OL,7,Fapproved the UK's participation in the
OL,8,FErasmus+ scheme for 2027 and opened
OL,9,Fthe door to begin negotiations on
OL,10,Fcloser alignment between the two
OL,11,Ftrading partners.
OL,13,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,14,FCarter
OL,16,FThe government claims the scheme,
OL,17,Fwhich was announced in December, could
OL,18,Fsee as many as 100,000 people in the
OL,19,FUK benefit from opportunities around
OL,20,Feducation, training, youth, culture
OL,21,Fand sport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FThe move to integrate with the EU
OL,7,Finternal electricity market is hoped
OL,8,Fto increase energy security for both
OL,9,Fblocs at a time when was in both
OL,10,FUkraine and the Middle East has caused
OL,11,Fchaos and uncertainty in the global
OL,12,Fenergy market.
OL,14,FThe commitment, along with integration
OL,15,Finto the EU's electricity market,
OL,16,Fcomes at a time when Labour have begun
OL,17,Fsignalling it favours closer UK-EU
OL,18,Fties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FIn her Mais lecture earlier this
OL,7,Fmonth, Chancellor Rachel Reeves said
OL,8,Fthe UK "should absolutely align" with
OL,9,FBrussels, describing the EU as the
OL,10,F"biggest prize" for boosting Britain's
OL,11,Fstagnant growth.
OL,13,FInfluential Labour Mayor of London
OL,14,FSadiq Khan went further, calling for a
OL,15,Ffull rejoining.
OL,17,FCalls from Labour for closer alignment
OL,18,Fare nevertheless in keeping with the
OL,19,Fgovernment's call for a Brexit reset,
OL,20,Faiming to stabilise and expand ties
OL,21,Fwith the EU.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FSo what's first on the reset agenda?
OL,8,FAnnounced in December, and formally
OL,9,Fapproved on Monday, the UK is set to
OL,10,Frejoin the Erasmus+ scheme from 2027.
OL,12,FTypically seen as student exchange
OL,13,Fprogrammes, the scheme encompasses far
OL,14,Fbroader parameters, funding these as
OL,15,Fwell as university staff and youth
OL,16,Fworkers doing teaching or training
OL,17,Fplacements, apprentices doing work
OL,18,Fplacements abroad, and young people
OL,19,Fdoing voluntary service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FThe EU distributes funds to
OL,7,Fparticipating partners and
OL,8,Fparticipants typically recieve a
OL,9,Fstipend to cover living expenses
OL,10,Fabroad.
OL,12,FThe UK's participation comes with a
OL,13,F#570 million yearly price tag, a
OL,14,Ffigure which the government said in
OL,15,FDecember included a negotiated 30%
OL,16,Fdiscount.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FCyprus' Deputy Minister for European
OL,7,FAffairs, Marilena Raouna, described
OL,8,Fstrengthening UK-EU relations as a
OL,9,F"key priority" of her country's EU
OL,10,Fpresidency.
OL,12,F"Today's decisions mark tangible
OL,13,Fprogress in delivering on the outcomes
OL,14,Fof the first EU`UK Summit held in May
OL,15,Flast year," she said.
OL,17,F"By promoting learning mobility via
OL,18,FErasmus+, we are advancing shared
OL,19,Finterests and reinforcing people-to-
OL,20,Fpeople ties, especially for our youth."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FElectricity markets
OL,8,FOn Monday, the European Council also
OL,9,Fagreed to kickstart negotiations on
OL,10,Fthe UK joining the EU's internal
OL,11,Felectricity market, a move both
OL,12,Fparties insist will reduce unnecessary
OL,13,Ffriction and lower energy bills.
OL,15,FTrade body Energy UK estimated in
OL,16,F2024, that this post-Brexit friction
OL,17,Fadded up to #370 million a year to the
OL,18,Fprice of purchasing energy from Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FThis is partly due to the different
OL,7,Fcosts both trading partners attach to
OL,8,Fcarbon emissions, creating tariffs
OL,9,Fbetween the two on account of the
OL,10,Fdisparity.
OL,12,FThe market works by allowing the free
OL,13,Fmovement of electricity from where it
OL,14,Fis generated in surplus to where there
OL,15,Fis increased demand, essentially
OL,16,Fallowing certain areas to benefit from
OL,17,Fcheaper prices being offered by EU
OL,18,Fcountries within the internal market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FThe current conflict in the Middle
OL,7,FEast and the effective closure of the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz have highlighted
OL,9,Fvulnerabilities in various countries'
OL,10,Fenergy supplies.
OL,12,FWere the UK to join the EU internal
OL,13,Felectricity market, the government
OL,14,Fhopes it would better protect supplies
OL,15,Ffrom short-term shocks.
OL,17,FThe European Council claimed any such
OL,18,Fagreement would lead to "dynamic
OL,19,Falignment of UK laws to EU rules",
OL,20,Fcreating a "level playing field
OL,21,Fbetween the parties."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FIt added: "Allowing the UK to
OL,7,Fparticipate in the EU's internal
OL,8,Felectricity market would improve the
OL,9,Fefficiency of the electricity trading
OL,10,Fbetween the parties, and facilitate
OL,11,Finvestments in electricity
OL,12,Finfrastructure, including renewable
OL,13,Felectricity generation that is
OL,14,Fnecessary to achieve both sides' net
OL,15,Fzero ambitions while safeguarding the
OL,16,Flevel playing field between the EU and
OL,17,Fthe UK."
OL,19,FThe cost of cohesion
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FParticipation in the EU's internal
OL,7,Felectricity market would however, come
OL,8,Fwith a cost.
OL,10,FNegotiations on how much the UK would
OL,11,Fcontribute to integrate with the EU
OL,12,Fmarket were also greenlit on Monday,
OL,13,Fwith the EU signalling it would seek
OL,14,Fto establish a "permanent mechanism"
OL,15,Ffor the UK to make an "appropriate
OL,16,Ffinancial contribution" to the EU's
OL,17,Fcohesion policy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FThe cohesion policy sees wealthier
OL,7,Fareas of the EU contribute so poorer
OL,8,Fregions can benefit from investment,
OL,9,Fwith the underlying theory being that
OL,10,Fa more economically balanced EU is a
OL,11,Fmore stable and politically
OL,12,Fsustainable one.
OL,14,FThe European Council said on Monday
OL,15,Fany participation from the UK in
OL,16,Fenergy markets would be contingent on
OL,17,Fthis financial agreement being reached
OL,18,Fsimultaneously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FIt said: "The agreement on the UK's
OL,7,Ffinancial contribution towards
OL,8,Freducing disparities between the EU
OL,9,Fregions by increasing the bloc's
OL,10,Feconomic, social and territorial
OL,11,Fcohesion is part of a consistent EU
OL,12,Fpolicy that couples the granting of
OL,13,Fmarket access to a third country with
OL,14,Fa fair financial contribution
OL,15,Freflecting the benefits derived from
OL,16,Fsuch access."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FAdding: "The financial contribution of
OL,7,Fthe UK should appropriately reflect
OL,8,Fthe relative size of the UK's economy
OL,9,Fand the proportion of the internal
OL,10,Fmarket in which the UK aims to
OL,11,Fparticipate in line with consistent EU
OL,12,Fpolicy."
