OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FCloser alignment or rejoining by the
OL,20,F"backdoor"?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FPrevious years have seen Labour shy
OL,7,Faway from calling for closer EU
OL,8,Falignment over fears of reigniting
OL,9,FBrexit battles and attacks claiming it
OL,10,Fwas trying to rejoin the EU.
OL,12,FResponding to Monday's announcement,
OL,13,FShadow Cabinet Office Minister Mike
OL,14,FWood said: "This deal goes far beyond
OL,15,Frejoining schemes like Erasmus."
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FHe added: "The UK is now being
OL,7,Fsubjected to pay into funding EU
OL,8,Finfrastructure, regeneration and cross-
OL,9,Fborder projects across Europe that
OL,10,Fbring no direct benefit to the British
OL,11,Fpublic.
OL,13,F"Keir Starmer appears ready to sign up
OL,14,Fto substantial payments to Brussels
OL,15,Fwithout securing meaningful returns -
OL,16,Fraising serious questions about value
OL,17,Ffor money for hardworking British
OL,18,Ftaxpayers.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,F"Taken together, this looks less like
OL,7,Fpragmatism and more like a backdoor
OL,8,Fway into rejoining the EU. Whilst
OL,9,FLabour are looking to reignite this
OL,10,Fdecade old debate, the Conservatives,
OL,11,Funder new leadership, have a plan to
OL,12,Ftake Britain forward."
OL,14,FFollowing today's approval, the EU
OL,15,FCommission will now open negotiations
OL,16,Fwith the UK on the two agreements in
OL,17,Fquestion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
