PN,30718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774962671
OL,3,CThree reasons why the UK could be
OL,4,Cgetting closer to EU neighbours
OL,6,FOnce negotiations are finalised, the
OL,7,Fagreements will have to be endorsed by
OL,8,Fthe Council before they can enter into
OL,9,Fforce.
